overview: What’s a better way to ring in a five-year anniversary than sharing three layers of cheesy admiration, sizzling hot passionate ground beef, all grilled to deep perfection in Taco Bell’s new Grilled Stuffed Corazon-a-rito?
tagline: There's Amor to Love with Taco Bell's new Grilled Stuffed Corazon-a-rito
title: Amor to Love
